{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_02_02",
  "title": "奥山すみれ 2話 笑顔のレポート",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_waterpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……どうですか？\n変じゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san… how’s this?\nDo I look weird?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_waterpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 7.533333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルのライブでも着たことあるんだろ？\n心配しなくても、似合ってるし可愛いと思うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve worn it for a TRINITYAiLE show before‚ right?\nDon’t worry‚ it suits you and I think it’s cute.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.372844413819351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_waterpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 17.566666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃ、初めて着る訳じゃないですけど……\nそんなにじっと見ないで下さい！　恥ずかしいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not wearing it for the first time‚ but…\nDon’t stare like that. It’s embarrassing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_waterpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 21.233333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "どうって聞かれたから、見たんだよ\nじっとは見てないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was looking because you asked how it looked.\nI’m not staring.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.949844692914915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "この格好で地上波に……ううっ\n知り合いに沢山見られちゃいます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looking like this on a TV… *whimper*\nLots of people I know will see me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "ははは恥ずかしいっちゃ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahhh that's pure blushin' embarrassing!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_waterpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 33.8666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "また山形弁が出てるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your Yamagata accent is coming out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_waterpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 36.9666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "い、いざどなった――いざとなったら\nやっぱり恥ずかしさが勝っちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I’m inna—When I’m in a pinch\nmy embarrassment wins out…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_waterpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 45.8666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい、偉そうなことを言ったのに……\nえへへ、ちょっぴり、震えてます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ I said I'm okay‚ but….\nEhehe‚ I’m trembling a little.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……\nなら、ちょっと待っていてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…\nIn that case‚ wait a minute.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_waterpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 58.2666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "え？　{user}さん\nどこに行くんですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? {user}-san?\nWhere are you going?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_waterpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 62.3666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "上にパーカーを羽織らせてもらうとか\n他のやり方を番組側と相談してみる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can wear a parka over the top or something.\nI’ll talk to the program staff about some other way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.98396352132161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それだと用意してもらった台本と\n違っちゃいますよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if we do that‚ it won’t fit with the script\nthey wrote for me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "ラストは私が海に飛び込んで、この施設の紹介と\nトリエルのライブの宣伝をしますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At the end I jump into the sea to introduce the park\nand advertise the TRINITYAiLE live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_waterpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 79.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そこは画を変更してもらえばいい\n海岸を歩きながらでも出来るはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can get them to change the scene for that bit.\nYou can just walk along the shore instead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_waterpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 85.3666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも、急にそんなことしたら\n{user}さんが怒られませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but if I do something like that all of a sudden‚\nwon’t you get scoled‚ {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロにも、お仕事をくれた\nスポンサーさんにもご迷惑が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hoshimi Productions‚ and the sponsors who gave us the job…\nI’ll be inconveniencing them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_waterpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 95.6333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "前にも言ったけど、君の一番の魅力は\n元気で明るいところなんだ。君は君らしくいてほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like I said before‚ your greatest appeal is\nthat you’re so lively and bright. I want you to be yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.76829664804103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そんな不安そうな顔で仕事をする方がダメだ\n君の水着姿よりも、笑顔を視聴者に届けよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no way you can work with such a nervous face.\nLet’s show the viewers your smiling face‚ not your swimsuit look.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.5405556678772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_waterpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 113.833333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、ちょっと話してくるから\nここで待っててくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I’ll just have a chat with them.\nWait here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.88854604085286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "ま、待って下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-wait!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　どうした？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? What’s the matter?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_waterpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 122.66666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "このままで大丈夫です！\n私、この衣装のままレポート出来ます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll be fine like this!\nI can do the report in this outfit!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "え？　でも、奥山さん――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? But‚ Okuyama-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_waterpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 130.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_02-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "お話したら、落ち着いてきました\n台本通り、この衣装でお仕事出来ます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m feeling calmer talking with you.\nI can do the job in this outfit‚ like in the script!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
